133typedef enum
134{
135 // Transfer is done without error, for ctrl it means status packet done
136 USB_XFER_DONE,
137 // For control transfer only, data stage is done without error
138 USB_XFER_DATA,
139 // Endpoint stall is set
140 USB_XFER_STALL,
141 // Endpoint stall is cleared
142 USB_XFER_UNSTALL,
143 // Transfer is aborted
144 USB_XFER_ABORT,
145 // Transfer is aborted because endpoint reset/disable
146 USB_XFER_RESET,
147 // There was an error
148 USB_XFER_ERROR
149}
